race.comment: KEEP ITA MYSTERY (1) flew home first-up without a trial in a strong return to racing. He's likely to get back from the draw again, but he rates highly on that effort and with further improvement expected. Parnham rides now having scored 3/4 when riding and he can storm over the top. SURF PATROL (14) comes here fresh with a couple of nice trials under his belt. He can sit handy from the inside draw and he boasts a strong record at this trip. Can play a leading role if he can be around his best first-up. SNIPPY WHICH (6) couldn't fend off the challengers late in the race when setting the tempo last start at this track and trip. Pike hops on board now replacing the apprentice hoop in a big push for his chances. Expecting him to be in this for a very long way. LET'S TALK (9) can improve on the first-up run where he just felt the pinch late. CHARINO (2) is better than we saw last start and getting out in trip now looks a good move.
